title: Artesian Restaurant
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located at Ojo Caliente Mineral Springs Resort and Spa. You can eat at the restaurant even if you are not staying at the resort. Vegan items and ones that can be made vegan include tacos, chili rellenos, burritos, maple nut granola, smoothies, and a tofu scramble. Others are tortilla soup, salads, black bean wrap, in-house-made garden burger w/o the bun and chipotle (ask for it on a tortilla or in a lettuce wrap because the other bread has egg), udon noodles, enchiladas and fajitas.
